,Recommended,293340,15852831,"Posted: 16 May, 2015",all,Fireslider,"I like this game it's very relaxing, looks good (apart from the character models). The controls are fine - diving is tricky at first but ok when you get the hang of it and, apart from that, the boats handle like boats. Things really pick up once you've got a sailboat. Trying to outrun pirates or a twister when you're short of time and your destination means your'e sailing into the wind? Yeah that works.All in all, The Good Life will easily provide enough hours of entertainment to justify the purchase. Go ahead."
